    "lyricsHtml": "\n[Intro] <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É pedra, é pedra, é pedra</span>\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É pedra de responsa</span>\n                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Mamãe eu volto prá ilha</span>\n                \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Nem que seja montado</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Na onça</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Quando fui</span>\n            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Na ilha maravilha</span>\n                      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Fui tratado como um paxá</span>\n                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Me deram arroz de cuxá</span>\n       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Água gelada da bilha</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Cozido de jurará</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Alavantú na quadrilha</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É pedra, é pedra, é pedra</span>\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>\n<span class=\"lyri