ass=\"lyric-line\">Me levaram no Boi-bumbá</span>\n          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Prá dançar</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu dancei!</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Me deram catuaba</span>\n           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Prá aprovar</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Aprovei!</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Me deram um cigarrim</span>\n         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Prá fumar</span>\n                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Menino, como eu gostei</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É pedra, é pedra, é pedra</span>\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É pedra de responsa</span>\n                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Mamãe eu volto prá ilha</span>\n                \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Nem que seja montado</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Na onça</span>\n\n( <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span> )\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É pedra, é pedra, é pedra</span>\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É pedra de responsa</span>\n                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Mamãe eu volto prá ilha</span>\n             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>\n<span class=